Class ReproducibleExperimentsInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • hesmlclient.ReproducibleExperimentsInfo

  • public class ReproducibleExperimentsInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the input data provided in a XML mfile in order to define a collection of reproducible experiments.
    Author:
    j.lastra
